/image/1d8d2e733cb14842c854e539e3760957/e66527f100758cc91cd42c18a62f28cd/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png&a=w%3D256%26h%3D97%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A46%3A10\",\"srcSet\":\"/_gatsby/image/1d8d2e733cb14842c854e539e3760957/e66527f100758cc91cd42c18a62f28cd/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png&a=w%3D256%26h%3D97%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A46%3A10 256w,/_gatsby/image/1d8d2e733cb14842c854e539e3760957/0c68165cf03d81d8c558beace86ca19e/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png&a=w%3D512%26h%3D194%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A46%3A10 512w,/_gatsby/image/1d8d2e733cb14842c854e539e3760957/aa024499fce45432cce050223b18d275/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-01.png&a=w%3D1024%26h%3D387%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A46%3A10 1024w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":387},\"alt\":\"How to set up SMTP Email for Magento 2 01\",\"className\":\"wp-image-1154 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"1\"}</script></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Navigate to the Magento Admin Panel and choose Stores &gt; Settings &gt; Configuration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. On the left side of the panel, select Store Email Address under General.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Go to the General Contact section to make adjustments to the default settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. In the Sender Name field, enter a name that you want to appear as the sender of any online mail newsletters. It is recommended to choose a name that is associated with the General Contact identity.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. In the Sender Email field, provide the corresponding online mail address.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>6. Repeat these steps for each email address that you want to use in the future.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>7. Don&#8217;t forget to click the Save button to apply the online mail settings for your M2 store.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 3: Maintain Your Sales Email Configuration</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To keep your sales online mail configuration up-to-date, follow these steps:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained wp-image-1156 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:1024px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height=&#x27;502&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1024&#x27;%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"2\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/_gatsby/image/9fd8fe0b05a647aac295da79e330b0f2/90f0c8048d7da1d9b83caa2506bdde5f/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png&amp;a=w%3D256%26h%3D126%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2023-03-07T09%3A47%3A20\" data-srcset=\"/_gatsby/image/9fd8fe0b05a647aac295da79e330b0f2/90f0c8048d7da1d9b83caa2506bdde5f/how-to-set-up-s