9%3A47%3A20 256w,/_gatsby/image/9fd8fe0b05a647aac295da79e330b0f2/134005b17ae4c2f7d5b975e0f42b644a/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png&a=w%3D512%26h%3D251%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A47%3A20 512w,/_gatsby/image/9fd8fe0b05a647aac295da79e330b0f2/6918cb49dd81c6ef28b7b595eb21ef35/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2-02.png&a=w%3D1024%26h%3D502%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-07T09%3A47%3A20 1024w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":502},\"alt\":\"How to set up SMTP Email for Magento 2 02\",\"className\":\"wp-image-1156 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"2\"}</script></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Set up the Magento sales system for your store.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Pay attention to the configuration of all related online mail messages to ensure that the sender&#8217;s information remains accurate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. In the admin panel, navigate to Sales, then select Sales online mail to access the settings edit page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Under Order, check that all sender information is correct.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. Email sending is a crucial factor in the success of any online merchant. After making the necessary adjustments, click the Save button to complete the configuration.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking to learn <strong><em>how to set up SMTP email for Magento 2</em></strong>, you may be interested in using the Magento 2 SMTP extension. The default SMTP in Magento 2 is great for reaching more customers and boosting sales, but it can often send online mails to spam or outbox folders instead of customers&#8217; inboxes. The Magento 2 SMTP extension can solve this problem and enhance the effectiveness of your email marketing efforts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To install the SMTP extension for your e-commerce store, simply log in to your admin panel, go to the &#8220;System&#8221; section, and choose &#8220;Web Setup Wizard.&#8221; Follow the steps provided to download and install the SMTP extension. For more information and details on how this extension can benefit your store, please visit our website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> As for the <a href=\"/how-to-create-bundle-product-in-magento-2/\">How to Create Bundle Product in Magento 2</a>, it is outside the scope of this description, but you can refer to Magento&#8217;s official documentation or seek the help of a developer for guidance on this topic.</p>\n<div class='sfsi_Sicons sfsi_Sicons_position_left' style='float: none; vertical-align: middle; text-align:left'><div style='margin:0px 8px 0px 0px; line-height: 24px'><span>Please follow and like us:</span></div><div class='sfsi_socialwpr'><div class='sf_fb_share sf_icon' style='text-align:left;vertical-align: middle;'><a  target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=/how-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2/' style='display:inline-block;'><img class='sfsi_wicon'  data-pin-nopin='true' alt='fb-share-icon' title='Facebook Share' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/fb_icons/en_US.svg' /></a></div><div class='sf_twiter sf_icon' style='display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;margin-left: 7px;'>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a target='_blank' rel='noopener' href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+set+up+SMTP+Email+for+Magento+2+https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fhow-to-set-up-smtp-email-for-magento-2%2F'style='display:inline-block' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img data-pin-nopin= true class='sfsi_wicon' src='https://webguru.dev/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/share_icons/Twitter_Tweet/en_US_Tweet.svg' alt='Tweet' title='Tweet' >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><